text: Roland Audenrieth (born 2 July 1979) is a German former ski jumper. In the World Cup he finished once among the top 10, with a tenth place from Zakopane in January 1998. He won the overall Continental Cup in the 1998/99 season. ==External links== * Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:German male ski jumpers
